1	#!/usr/bin/env python3
2	"""A very light localhost viewer for a delegate work_dir.
3	
4	Reads the same <work_dir>/.delegate/ state the MCP writes (no new deps, stdlib
5	only) and serves a single auto-refreshing page showing the agent roster, the
6	shared blackboard, the live event log, and total spend. A message box lets YOU
7	post onto the message bus (messages.jsonl) that agents read and reply to
8	via their post_message tool — your channel into the swarm.
9	
10	    python viewer.py <work_dir> [port]      # default port 7878
11	
12	Run as a separate process from the MCP server; they share state through the
13	files on disk.
14	"""
